abstract: HOUSTON, Oct. 26 (AP)--Earl Campbell scored on runs of 55 and 3 yards in the second half today and became the second runner in National Football League history to gain 200 yards in successive games as the Houston Oilers routed the Cincinnati Bengals, 23-3.
